<BaseLayout
  title="How It Works | FreeOnlyFanz"
  description="How FreeOnlyFanz organizes curated creator picks, categories, and outbound links."
  canonicalPath="/how-it-works/"
>
  <article class="info-page container">
    <header class="info-page-header">
      <p class="info-eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h1>How It Works</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="info-page-body">
      <p>
        We group creator pages into sections and categories—new picks, trials, featured shelves, and broader free browsing—so
        you can skim what fits your mood.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you open a profile card, you leave FreeOnlyFanz for the creator’s page or offer. We do not host that content
        here. What you see off-site is between you and that site’s rules.
      </p>
      <p>
        Picks are curated for browsing quality, not a promise about every page. Use your judgment, read terms on destination
        sites, and only continue if you are 18+ where you live.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
